Delete a Report

You can delete a selected report from the Reports tab or from its run page.

Available in: Essentials, Group, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED

* To delete reports in My Personal Custom Reports folder: Create and Customize Reports
* To delete reports in public folders: Manage Reports in Public Folders

To delete a report:

* Next to the report, select | Delete.
* Click Delete.
* Click OK.

Deleted reports are moved to the Recycle Bin. You also canâ€™t delete reports used by dashboard widgets or reporting snapshots unless you first delete the dashboard widget or reporting snapshot.
